

=Bio=

Kennet Miriam (UK). Economist and member of  Mansfield College and the  Environmental Change Institute at Oxford University. She is the CEO, director and  co-founder of the Green Economics Institute. Moreover, she is founder and  editor of the International Journal of Green Economics and The Green Economist.      


